      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification test suite and version-controlled source. Commercial solver with published validation history acceptable at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used; solver has documented V&V test suite, ISO 9001 quality management certification, and version-controlled releases. Solver regression tests documented in release notes. Requirement met."
