      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documentation of test article representativeness. At MRL 2, use of FDA benchmark geometry with documented manufacturing tolerances acceptable.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic pump test article manufactured to published dimensional specifications (Hariharan et al. 2011). Geometric tolerances ±0.05 mm documented. Sample-to-sample variability not formally characterized; single representative pump used per FDA benchmark protocol. Acceptable at MRL 2."
    },
