    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scope. Validation against FDA generic pump experimental data demonstrates NIH prediction accuracy within 8.3% mean relative error, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all evaluated operating conditions. Discretization error is well-characterized with GCI < 2.5%. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Assessment accepted.",
